  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Now it is time to select the role! There are 6 different roles available
    from which you can choose. The players must decide amongst themselves which role
    they want to play with. To do so, they can click on each role to see the description
    about them and their role in the project. \n\nWhen you open any of the roles
    you would see \u201CRole Play Elements\u201D. These are best practices known
    to your role, since you have knowledge in the field. By sharing this with others,
    you would be able to help the group progress and make better decisions. \r\n\nFurthermore,
    you will find how many resources your role has for each round. Not all roles
    have the same number of resources. Depending upon the participation of each role,
    they are allotted with a certain number of resources per round.\r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
