  m_text: "Read the following text aloud after the second week in phase 2 has been
    dealt with.\v\r\n\nBest Practice: \"I think the solution-neutral description
    of the functions within the framework of the functional hierarchy is great. This
    has a huge reuse value. Especially the functions for control and operation via
    smartphone can be used for the upcoming development of the smart oven. \"\r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
