  m_text: 'Read the following text aloud after the first phase event.

    Best Practice:
    "Hey, in the "Cook-Blade" (Thermomix development) the traceability of the requirements
    saved our asses. As you know, in the middle of the project the topic of "US expansion"
    suddenly came up and the Cook Blade was also to be sold in the States. Because
    we had consistency, the change analysis was easy for us."

'
