  m_text: 'As an electronics developer, you are the specialist for the E&E (Electrical
    and Electronics) components. You work on the architecture of the system from
    an electrical engineering point of view. Your skills are particularly in demand
    when it comes to finding and testing electronic components. In doing so, you
    coordinate closely with the mechanics and software colleagues. Occasionally,
    you also support colleagues in overarching issues.


    Number of Resources
    available per round: 9'
