  m_text: "Read the following text aloud after the first week in phase 2.\u200B\r\n\r\n\u200B\nBest
    Practice: \"Behaviour? Yes, we did this once in our last project \"Roast-Master\"
    (multi-function microwave) for the new customer function \"external baking start\".
    That was a day's work for the whole team, but afterwards, it was clear to everyone
    what the function should be able to do and we didn't have to deal with it a single
    other time in the course of development.\"\u200B\r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
