  m_text: "Read the following text aloud after the first week resolved in Phase 3.\n\nBest
    Practice: \"I would have wished for such a benefit analysis for the \"Roast-Master\"
    (multifunction microwave). Today nobody knows why the part was developed the
    way it looks now. We have 3 control units in there, which is total nonsense because
    nobody took the time to look at alternatives, let alone document it.\"\u200B\r\n\u200B"
